                            <comment id="15191388" author="vrodionov" created="Fri, 11 Mar 2016 18:59:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Partially resolved (in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14123&quot; title=&quot;HBase Backup/Restore Phase 2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-14123&quot;&gt;HBASE-14123&lt;/a&gt;-v11 patch). &lt;/p&gt;

